					<p class="text-sm font-light sm:max-md:pt-2">
					  <b class="font-poppins text-lg block"
						>The ETHPrague Conference 2024</b
					  >
					  is a major gathering in the blockchain community, with
					  notable attendees such as Gavin Wood (founder of Polkadot
					  and co-founder of Ethereum), Vitalik Buterin (founder of
					  Ethereum), and Mihai Alisie (co-founder of Ethereum). It's
					  also a historic moment, marking the first time that Vitalik
					  and Gavin will appear together on stage for talks and
