					  generative artwork based on a unique code, producing 128
					  distinct editions, each a one-of-a-kind piece. The work
					  evolves in real time, displayed on screens in an endless
					  loop, exploring the organic spread of patterns through an
					  intricate, ever-changing composition. Each frame builds upon
